<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<section xml:id="attendance-policy" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title> Attendance</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>Regular attendance is required. You are responsible for any notes or work missed due absence. 
    <em>If you miss more than four classes, you will be dropped from this class and assigned a grade 
            of ABS, as appropriate.</em>
    </p>
  </introduction>
</section>